Here are the steps to becoming a game developer:
1. Download Unity.
2. Take the Unity course Create with Code: https://learn.unity.com/course/create-with-code?_ga=2.128853388.182606264.1665666231-1139320979.1665666231
3. Make the game of your dreams.
4. Upload to itch.io, Steam, or really any other game platform.
